<h2>Related Plans & Dependencies</h2>

<ul>
<li><strong>Plan E.1 (AI Chat System):</strong> Phase 3 widget development begins; depends on successful message persistence validation</li>
<li><strong>Plan F.1 (Daily Audit Infrastructure):</strong> First full test of three-agent architecture; success validates future daily workflows</li>
