</ul>

<h2>Notes for Developers</h2>

<ul>
<li><strong>Testing Access:</strong> Message persistence testing requires ZeroTier access or local development environment with valid credentials</li>
<li><strong>Widget Scaffold:</strong> Create non-functional UI first; implement API calls on Dec 30-31</li>
<li><strong>Daily Audit:</strong> This is first automated run of three-agent pipeline; document any issues for improvement</li>
<li><strong>If Blocked:</strong> Message persistence testing blocked without access? Create dummy test data in database and verify widget UI rendering instead</li>
